</style><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="ja" dir="ltr"> ⋆⋆⋆⋆ 主题曲标题和主唱发布⋆⋆⋆⋆⋆<br> 𓈒𓏸𓂃<br>梅森德斯<br>“七奈的壮举。星町水成，佐久间。”<br> 𓂃◌𓈒𓐍 <a href="https://twitter.com/MAISONdes_6half?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@MAISONdes_6half</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/suisei_hosimati?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@suisei_hosimati</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/_Sakuma0331?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@_Sakuma0331</a><br><br>期待歌曲完整版ˎˊ˗<br><br>电影“ <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E3%83%88%E3%83%A9%E3%83%9A%E3%82%B8%E3%82%A6%E3%83%A0?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Trapezium</a> ”于 5 月 10 日星期五上映<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4ab.png" alt="💫" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/GoRYYQYgnV">pic.twitter.com/GoRYYQYgnV</a></p> — 官方电影《Trapezium》 (@trapezium_movie) <a href="https://twitter.com/trapezium_movie/status/1755879207706501627?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 2 月 9 日</a></blockquote><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="ja" dir="ltr"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2604.png" alt="☄" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />注意<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2604.png" alt="☄" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><br><br> //<br>电影《Trapezium》于5/10(星期五)上映<br>我负责主题曲<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2604.png" alt="☄" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2728.png" alt="✨" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><