S活动等。可能是因为对ANYCOLOR公司的批评而接连发生</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ Nijisanji en（新的）附属VTUBER暂停发行，SNS活动等。" src="https://p2y.jp/nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-are-suspending-streaming-and-sns-activities-one-after-another-possibly-due-to-criticism-of-anycolor/embed/#?secret=26pxUVLOFJ#?secret=hMbLlzCIvu" data-secret="hMbLlzCIvu" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="JpRDCt17ry"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/studio-nekomata-ended-handling-of-nijisanji-related-goods-due-to-protest-against-selen-tatsuki-terminated/">在取消塞伦·鲁吉苏（Seren Ryugetsu）的合同后，Nekomata Studio Nekomata已停止处理与Nijisanji相关的商品以抗议？</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Studio Nekomata 已停止处理与 Nijisanji 相关的商品。这是 Seren Ryugetsu 合同被取消后的抗议吗？” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/studio-nekomata-ended-handling-of-nijisanji-related-goods-due-to-protest-against-selen-tatsuki-terminated/embed/#?secret=NifXcz8pd6#?secret=JpRDCt17ry" data-secret="JpRDCt17ry" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="XSpehH79Bc"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/wikipedia-x-account-post-a-criticizing-nijisanji-anycolor-as-a-black-company/">Wikipedia的X帐户发表了一篇文章，批评Nijisanji和AnyColor作为黑人公司？</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ Wikipedia X帐户发表了一篇批评Nijisanji/AnyColor作为黑人公司的帖子”  -  P2Y.JP" src="https://p2y.jp/wikipedia-x-account-post-a-criticizing-nijisanji-anycolo