nji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-contract-violations-and-misrepresentations-on-sns/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">反复违反合同，误导合同，误导性以及对SNS的虚假陈述和诉讼</a></em>终止与Seren Ryugetsu终止的合同。&#39;&#39;此外，对该公司的愤怒批评，包括<a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-announced-minor-financial-impact-from-nijisanji-en-new-selen-tatsuki-terminated/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">IR宣布<em>对业务绩效的影响极为较小的消息，</em></a>发生在海外VTUBER观众和粉丝中。</p><p>此外，据称是Seren Ryugetsu的表演者/声优模特的VTuber <strong>Dokibird</strong>的订阅人数自2月5日起迅速增加，截至2月8日20:45，已记录约418,000人。已经完成。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="VpBzZ2dwzu"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/selen-tatsuki-supposed-actor-vtuber-dokibird-has-been-return-streaming-127300-watched/">大约127,300人观看Vtuber Dokibird，Seren Ryugetsu /语音模型的语音模型</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“约 127,300 人观看了 VTuber Dokibird 的《Return Broadcast》，据称该节目是 Seren Ryugetsu 的表演者/声优” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/selen-tatsuki-supposed-actor-vtuber-dokibird-has-been-return-streaming-127300-watched/embed/#?secret=KUJw0SdkWk#?secret=VpBzZ2dwzu" data-secret="VpBzZ2dwzu" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><div class="nvmtw65c686a196f1f" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
